                                      Introduction

      Welcome to our site.

         In a time when many federal agencies are downsizing through reduction
         in force, federal employees need information about career transition,
         federal and non-federal employment, retirement, buyouts, RIF, benefits,
         going back to school, and other transiti onal tools, such as starting a
         business. This site pulls all this information together in a
         user-friendly format. Please feel free to provide any comments you may
         wish to pbrunner@doleta.gov.

